snippet.title: Amber Heard EXPOSED for LYING about ARREST RECORD!?
snippet.description:
Apologies for the error at the end of the video, it was meant to cut off. 
CHARITY DONATIONS LINK: https://www.pledge.to/art-of-elysium-charity-stream-6744
Amber Heard in my opinion, has been caught in several lies. It is not in Heard's character to be able to tell the truth. In this video we chat about how Heard's lawyer claims there are NO prior arrests or trouble with the law, with Heard. It's funny to hear them say this, considering Amber has a HUGE past with legal issues. In AH's eyes, and the eyes of many others, it is always Depp's fault. We want Justice for Johnny Depp; I believe Depp will prevail and get justice, in the Virginia trial.
